      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though it shows a few minor stone chips consistent with careful highway use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with premium leather upholstery that remains soft and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system, functions exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule and recent fluid changes. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension provides a firm yet comfortable ride with no unusual noises. This car has been garage-kept and loved, offering a turn-key experience for its next owner. Complete with a full service history and two sets of keys.",
